---

<section class="py-16 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 transition-colors duration-300">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-6xl">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12">
      <div class="md:w-1/2">
        <img
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1460925895917-afdab827c52f?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1415&q=80"
          alt="Proyeksi 5 Tahun"
          class="rounded-xl shadow-lg w-full"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="md:w-1/2">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800 dark:text-white mb-6">
          Proyeksi <span class="text-primary">5 Tahun</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6">
          Dengan model bisnis yang sudah teruji, outlet PITCAR Service menunjukkan pertumbuhan yang konsisten setiap
          tahunnya.
        </p>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="bg-primary p-2 rounded-full mr-4 shrink-0">
              <i class="fas fa-chart-line text-white"></i>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-white">Order Bertumbuh</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Volume order meningkat signifikan tiap tahun</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="bg-primary p-2 rounded-full mr-4 shrink-0">
              <i class="fas fa-money-bill-wave text-white"></i>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-white">Omzet Meningkat</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Pertumbuhan omzet rata-rata 25-30% per tahun</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="bg-primary p-2 rounded-full mr-4 shrink-0">
              <i class="fas fa-percentage text-white"></i>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-white">Profit Margin Lebih Tinggi</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Efisiensi operasional meningkatkan profit margin</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
